                  </hi>. I was standing at my door at half-past twelve o'clock, on the 3rd of May—I saw the prisoner making some progress up the court, from Half Moon-passage—the prosecutor was running after him, and I took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was almost starved, I was two days without food—I saw the handkerchief hanging out of the pocket, and I was tempted to take it.</p>
